ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdaf50470d067664f25ea5a5b2826028b7478ab","tid":914150,"uid":162112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T00:46:54.000Z","msg":"琴日發生左你講嘅野<br />\n佢琴日飛左我 話失望太多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我力挽狂瀾都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fd54c789156e9ba2a303bed317c2edc58eea64","tid":914150,"uid":169381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T00:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fec216943317d3863d55f92512f89db2a78bf73a","tid":914150,"uid":162112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"437a84d9e3f88fd00d9b772701599836bb10454a","tid":914150,"uid":162895,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"巴打我同樣情況, 岩岩散左<br />\n到失去個刻先至反醒自己, 先自覺傷害左對方幾多次, 令佢失望幾多次<br />\n最後都係連一面都唔肯見, 就分左手了<br />\n事隔三星期佢已經有一段新感情, 但我都只有痛恨自己辜負佢,傷害佢太多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T00:49:50.000Z","msg":"真係到冇左果下先識反省<br />\n對佢黎已經太遲<br />\n分手果日我同佢講晒我反省<br />\n佢話半年先你咁講我就跟你一世<br />\n分左手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478c55a875a95d748574ce1649547d867fcf0156","tid":914150,"uid":205109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e1347f04ccfc74c3d93b9c12eb4579d8990e44","tid":914150,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot